s://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-boost-your-woocommerce-store-results-with-oceanwp-and-premmerce/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"premmerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16812:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-boost-your-woocommerce-store-results-with-oceanwp-and-premmerce/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/oceanwp_banner_2.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"How to boost your WooCommerce store results with OceanWP and Premmerce?\" alt=\"How to boost your WooCommerce store results with OceanWP and Premmerce?\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>Are you sure you’re making the most of your OceanWP theme? Premmerce is here to demonstrate how to amplify your users’ navigation and products presentation and as a result sell more with the help of its plugins. <br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you got interested, read on and learn about features we developed and integrated into the OceanWP theme (which is one of the most popular themes in WordPress!). And, of course, we couldn&#8217;t but provide you with some real-life experience, so take your time and check out our OceanWP based <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">online store demo version here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Improving navigation features </h2>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Product Filter</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin is a handy and flexible tool for managing filters for WooCommerce products. The main plugin features are a single widget that controls the display of all available filters and a well-designed caching system that improves the load speed, outperforming the standard WooCommerce filters.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Advanced SEO settings for filters and the ability to control the filter URLs formation are available in the Premium version of the plugin. You can learn about all the plugins features <a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-product-filter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-1024x675.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380624\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-1024x675.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-300x198.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-768x506.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, you can view the OceanWP demo integrated with  Premmerce filters <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/clothes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Variation Swatches</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Premmerce WooCommerce Variation Swatches will help you to visualize the product variations as well as enable your customers to buy a variational product from the product catalog.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can learn about all the plugin features <a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-variation-swatches/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Display in the product archive:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-1024x657.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380723\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-1024x657.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-300x193.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-768x493.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2.png 1556w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Product variations are presented by colors and labels:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-1024x582.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380724\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-1024x582.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-300x171.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-768x437.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Product variations are presented by images:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-1024x563.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380725\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-1024x563.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-300x165.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-768x422.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also view the OceanWP demo with the Premmerce swatches set up  <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/clothes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Product Search</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Premmerce Search turns ‘product search’ into a live search and also provides additional search results using spell correction.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can learn about all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-product-search/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-1024x474.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380729\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-1024x474.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-300x139.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-768x356.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also view the OceanWP demo with set up Premmerce search <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Frequently Bought Together</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Premmerce Frequently Bought Together will help you to create product sets that will increase sales through discounts in a bundle. This is one of the main marketing tools used by Amazon to raise the average check. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You  can learn about all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-frequently-bought-together/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-1024x608.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380746\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-1024x608.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-300x178.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-768x456.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6.png 1403w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Please view the OceanWP demo with Premmerce Frequently Bought Together <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/clothes/shirts/flowy-blouse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tools for usability improvement</h2>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Wishlist</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>A wishlist is a tool that will allow your customers to choose and save products for future purchases and to share them with their friends. Just review wishlists and influence your customers’ by offering bargains and super deals based on the collected information.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can learn about all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-1024x581.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380753\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-1024x581.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-300x170.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-768x435.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce plugin addon &#8211; Premmerce Product Comparison</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Product comparison is a tool that will enable your customers to choose the best product, decide and make a purchase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/premmerce-main-plugin-woocommerce-plugins-bundle/#reading-progress-title-4\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-1024x567.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380758\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-1024x567.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-300x166.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-768x425.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Brands</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin allows you to create an unlimited number of brands that can be assigned to products for better cataloging, product search and additional opportunities for marketing and product promotion by brands.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Discover all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/premmerce-woocommerce-brands-free-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-1-1024x606.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380764\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-1-1024x606.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-1-300x178.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-1-768x455.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also view the OceanWP demo with set up Premmerce brands <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/brands/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce Woocommerce Multi-currency</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Premmerce Woocommerce Multi-currency plugin allows you to start a multi-currency store with flexible settings and a number of additional unique features.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-1024x531.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380765\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-1024x531.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-300x156.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-768x398.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To display the currency switcher in the top bar, just add the [multicurrency] shortcode to the Content field in the theme Customizer:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/13-1024x581.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-381642\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/13-1024x581.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/13-300x170.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/13-768x436.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can learn about all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/premmerce-woocommerce-multi-currency/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Optimizing performance &#8211; Premmerce Performance Optimizer</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>WooCommerce often doesn’t handle a number of performance issues encountered by the stores with a large product base without cache and third-party optimization. Thus, we’ve studied this problem, and as a result, we’ve designed the plugin that automatically optimizes your online store operations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, we’ve tested the performance of the OceanWP theme with 500k of products and the work of the Premmerce Performance Optimizer plugin. We’ve created the website where you can personally test and view all plugins in action.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The test results are shown in the diagram:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Test 1 &#8211; OceanWP + Premmerce  plugins</li><li>Test 2 &#8211; OceanWP + Premmerce plugins + Premmerce Performance Optimizer</li><li>Test 3 &#8211; OceanWP + Premmerce plugins + Premmerce Performance Optimizer + WP Rocket</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12-1024x634.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380781\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12-1024x634.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12-300x186.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12-768x475.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12.png 1380w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can read more about the test results and plugin features on this <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"page (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-performance-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\">page</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Additional plugins that don’t affect the store display</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also be interested in some  other Premmerce  plugins that will contribute to the flexible setup of your store:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce WooCommerce Permalink Manager (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-permalink-manager-remove-shop-product-product-category-url/\" target=\"_blank\">Premmerce WooCommerce Permalink Manager</a></strong> is developed to improve the current WooCommerce URL configuration features and provide your store with better display options and additional SEO capabilities to adhere to WooCommerce SEO Audit standards.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-redirect-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce Redirect Manager (opens in a new tab)\">Premmerce Redirect Manager</a></strong> enables you to create 301 and 302 redirects and to set up the automatic redirects for the deleted products in the WooCommerce store.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce User Roles (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/wordpress-custom-user-roles/\" target=\"_blank\">Premmerce User Roles</a></strong> &#8211;  this plugin has been developed for creating user roles from the WordPress admin area and assigning the arbitrary access rights to them. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-customers-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce WooCommerce Customers Manager (opens in a new tab)\">Premmerce WooCommerce Customers Manager</a></strong> extends the standard user list and the edit user page in WordPress and adds the customer data from WooCommerce. This is the main customer management plugin from Premmerce, which we constantly improve by adding new features, considering the needs of its users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://premmerce.com/premmerce-woocommerce-wholesale-pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce Woocommerce Wholesale Pricing (opens in a new tab)\">Premmerce Woocommerce Wholesale Pricing</a></strong> allows you to add prices to products for each user roles.     </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-seo-addon-yoast/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"WooCommerce SEO Addon (opens in a new tab)\">WooCommerce SEO Addon</a></strong> plugin extends the functionality of Yoast SEO for microdata management and provides all the instruments you need for your store’s SEO improvement.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Premmerce plugins pricing</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The free version is available in all Premmerce plugins and in many cases, it’s sufficient for dealing with a variety of issues. You can find all of them in the official <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/premmerce/#content-plugins\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"WordPress marketplace (opens in a new tab)\">WordPress marketplace</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some plugins offer Premium versions that complement and expand their basic capabilities. Also, the users of Premium versions get technical support and regular updates. Our team often add new features to the existing plugins, so your store is always trendy and functional as a result.  The price of Premium versions ranges from $ 45 to $ 65. Please, have a look at Premium versions in our marketplace.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Premmerce Suite</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to improve your OceanWP based online stores at once with all or most Premmerce plugins, we’ve prepared for you the <a href=\"https://premmerce.com/pricing/\">Premmerce Suite</a>, which provides the access to all the premium versions at a price just above the cost of 2 plugins.  Check it out!</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-boost-your-woocommerce-store-results-with-oceanwp-and-premmerce/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30p